<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She returned to the TOWIE scene for the first time in nine years earlier this month.</p>

<p>And Amy Childs proved there's no rest for the wicked as she filmed more scenes for the ITVBe show alongside Courtney Green in Essex on Friday.</p>

<p>The reality TV icon, 30, looked effortlessly chic for a day of go-karting with her co-stars as she styled a baggy white shirt with a cream trilby hat.</p>

