<p>Dressing down her look, the mother-of-two teamed classic skinny jeans with comfy white trainers.</p>

<p>Huge circular-framed shades ensured she shielded her eyes from the sun, while gold dangle earrings brought the glamour to her outfit.</p>

<p>Former junior PA Courtney, 25, put on a casual display in a clingy white playsuit, tied in with a denim shirt wrapped around her waist.</p>

